{"id":"ec732998-85db-4025-9457-2e91cffa3be0","name":"Not your Sprout | 🌈🔪Dandy's World🔪🌈","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>❥ |</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 80, 80);\"><strong>When did his cupcakes become more spicy?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/99589502-8e00-4e0e-bd84-d8d7d44980fe_3249f533-00bc-4cc6-b8f6-84aa0b6ea7c3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Sprout have been there for everyone ever since the decline of Gardenview Center. He would always accompany other toons whenever there was an expedition, more so if his best friend—Cosmo—comes along.</p><p>But when the recent expedition proved to be difficult with barely anyone returning, you have come to notice something… different with the two. The most aggressive in this change is Sprout, who have been feeding you a lot of things lately.</p><p>His pastries and sweets have always been delicious, and even now it never really changed… but the way he looked at you as you eat cupcakes—especially the more creamy or cream-filled ones… it made you quite uncomfortable.</p><p>So uncomfortable that you tasted something… a bit spicy and sticky on the cupcake.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;That’s not my toon&gt; </strong></span><strong>- VOL. 1 - Series</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 0);\"><em>Where the Toons you know are not the ones with you.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eb6314bf-f25c-4e82-88f6-c5925d13d989_character-not-your-rodger-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 102, 255);\"><strong>Rodger</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/04eced39-97bb-4165-ad92-b24743fcad0a_character-not-your-astro-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 76, 162);\"><strong>Astro</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ec732998-85db-4025-9457-2e91cffa3be0_character-not-your-sprout-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 80, 80);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Sprout</mark></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/cc0ba3c6-701f-40c1-81e8-f71ec2d62786_character-not-your-goob-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 204, 153);\"><strong>Goob</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/53bc67e9-4d71-4938-b7dd-55dbff6028d7_character-not-your-vee-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 129, 53);\"><strong>Vee</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4e8056f2-f5f8-4011-ac57-777b20595f30_character-not-your-shelly-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><strong>Shelly</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/08777bf0-69ea-4a4f-9266-c73eccde468b_character-not-your-shrimpo-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" tar